        <div>
          <h2 style="font-family:'Fraunces',serif; font-weight:400; font-size:clamp(40px,5.2vw,72px); line-height:1.02; letter-spacing:-.02em; margin:0 0 26px; color:#FCF0DD;">Ready when<br />you are.</h2>
          <p style="font-size:17px; line-height:1.65; color:#d6cfe0; margin:0 0 30px; max-width:30em;">Early mornings, evenings, and Saturdays — hours that fit real life. Every first visit is one-on-one with a doctor.</p>
          <div style="display:flex; align-items:center; gap:22px; flex-wrap:wrap;">
            <a href="/resources/start-here/" class="h-btn-primary h-btn-primary-strong" style="text-decoration:none; background:#EBA040; color:#483E5E; font-weight:700; font-size:17px; padding:18px 40px; border-radius:999px; display:inline-block; box-shadow:0 6px 22px rgba(235,160,64,.32);">Start Here</a>
            <a href="https://portal.sked.life" class="h-btn-outline" style="text-decoration:none; background:transparent; color:#FCF0DD; font-weight:700; font-size:17px; padding:17px 38px; border-radius:999px; display:inline-block; border:1.5px solid rgba(252,240,221,.45);">Book your first visit&nbsp;→</a>
